reviewText: It's what it says it is. It's hard, but I like them.

I love Jillian micheals.... I have her body shred and swear by it.  These two new dvd's were complicated and hard to follow.  I hate to say it, but I would recommend these workouts.  Almost all her other ones are amazing though.
Be prepared to sweat and work hard I would recommend beginners start with one of her other videos
